Sure, here are some examples:

1. Planiramo da se vratimo sa *odmora* nakon dve nedelje. (We plan to return from *vacation* after two weeks.)
2. *Odlazak* na fakultet je bio veliki izazov za mene. (Going to college was a big challenge for me.)
3. *Odlaska* na putovanje se mnogo radujem. (I'm really looking forward to *going* on a trip.)
4. Nakon *odlaska* njegovog tima, njegov se stil rada promenio. (After *his team's departure*, his work style changed.)
5. On je otišao na vrlo važan sastanak, a njegov *odlazak* će biti odlučujući. (He went to a very important meeting, and his *departure* will be decisive.)
6. Proslava *odlaska* u penziju se planira za kraj meseca. (A celebration for *retirement* is planned for the end of the month.)
7. Njegov *odlazak* iz grada će mi jako nedostajati. (I will miss him a lot after *he leaves* the city.)
8. *Odlazak* u bioskop je uvek dobra ideja za provod. (Going to the cinema is always a good idea for entertainment.)

Note: In each sentence, the word "odlaska" is highlighted with a star (*).